<span style="color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">一、为什么要做前期服务报告</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">帮助客户找问题症结</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">提供解决问题的策略</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">有效控制成本和风险</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">助力实现利益最大化</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">二、项目分析报告</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">三、服务计划书</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">四、策略分析报告</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">适用于客户主动寻求争议解决方案</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(79, 129, 189);">五、法律咨询意见</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">适用于潜在客户的非正式性接触</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">05</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; b